theorem Topology.P1_P2_P3_of_isOpen {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] {A : Set X}
    (hA : IsOpen A) :
    (Topology.P1 A) ∧ (Topology.P2 A) ∧ (Topology.P3 A) := by
  exact
    And.intro
      (Topology.P1_of_isOpen (A := A) hA)
      (And.intro
        (Topology.P2_of_isOpen (A := A) hA)
        (Topology.P3_of_isOpen (A := A) hA))
